就自自然冇興趣賭<br />\n<br />\n直到上年世界杯先第一次去買波<br />\n明明乜都唔識就偏偏越買越大<br />\n由50蚊買到2500蚊一場<br />\n<br />\n可能2500蚊果場印象太深刻<br />\n比利時對日本買比利時淨贏<br />\n我望住個電視日本贏2:0時即刻機都熄埋冇眼睇<br />\n<br />\n到第二朝起身見到竟然唔輸追返之前輸果D<br />\n當見識到可以咁大變化好似過山車咁唔穩定<br />\n我就立左決心過左世界盃刪左馬會app<br />\n<br />\n仲有就係...師傅教落<br />\n賭可以賭，麻煩都好，去馬會落注<br />\n太方便好易做錯事"},{"pid":"f2d66e3d45ee5581f6db388d9ed2be2452be90e4","tid":980852,"uid":160528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"839bec5c7aa39e44254bc104dd344749a8a49ef4","tid":980852,"uid":81273,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T20:32:57.000Z","msg":"重心輸、平注炒、重注針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T00:59:12.000Z","msg":"本post宗旨"},{"pid":"5e689db8a9b69eae479e1596f8a5e21060d160ed","tid":980852,"uid":160528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d600e8b0b61de744f2641854039f2a9f86f91a83","tid":980852,"uid":231116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56b71e86e7d2e9f17eaf85fcb44b6dcddea278a1","tid":980852,"uid":160528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f8a060d289c9ddcec58c5ddaafb134ee090aed1","tid":980852,"uid":117509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T20:26:06.000Z","msg":"首先你睇少D波<br />\n搵其他野搞下先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T20:29:42.000Z","msg":"其實一開始原意想分散自己注意先玩下 點知依家走火入魔<br />\n<br />\n依家都逼自己搵其他野做下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T20:36:39.000Z","msg":"明白嘅 心靈波中 落飛就針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係會好激心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T00:59:36.000Z","msg":"唉 諗住試下手氣 就出事"},{"pid":"1da9a24994bd2c740231d0aaf60b141be45ca194","tid":980852,"uid":160528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00c94677ba632c480e592679ba31749ef4532867","tid":980852,"uid":117509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T20:44:14.000Z","msg":"我就一直都唔會賭既<br />\n因為我條命生得好<br />\n<br />\n賭乜輸乜，逢